Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.46,0:00:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H313395&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.20,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed with his father by the evil organisation GOD,\NJin Keisuke is revived as Kamen Rider X.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mission: to preserve peace and justice by\Nfighting the mysterious agency known as GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Terror!\NKing Dark's Vengeance!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:02:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...Still gave me a fright, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want with this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are you ok?\N-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you look just like--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the daughter of that famous Dr. Yáng?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:03:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems so. Dr. Yáng probably has a\Npiece of Dr. Nanbara's blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD have already killed him and his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do they want with the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They must think she's got the blueprint piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, chief... How'd it be\Nif she stayed here a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.80,0:03:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure! I'll look after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright folks, the young lady's\Nstaying with us for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's great!\N-We're gonna have fun!\N-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so cute, it's gonna be like\Nhaving a blooming flower in the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Mako, don't you think she's\Nhaving a little too much fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,For real... But that's Keisuke for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants today to be all about\Nspoiling Dr. Yáng's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone sounds jealous!\NHere, cool off with these!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank you!\N-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy yourself, Jin Keisuke... It won't last!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we eat lunch here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Seconded!\N-Seconded!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird, he was with us before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Whatever, let's eat!\N-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-Keisuke!\N-Hi! Sorry, I had to check something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-Just a bit dizzy...\N-Dizzy? We'll get you to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll be alright after a little rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest, here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, you should let her use yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. It's the closest. C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...Alright, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:05:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I just need some sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave me alone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this kid up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-She's a thief!\N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-So, now you know...\N-Wh-who--?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How lucky you girls are,\Nseeing my true face...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-Help, help!!\N-Someone, quick!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:08:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,GOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, I am Centipede Yáng\NGuìfēi of GOD's Villain Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Dr. Yáng's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Yáng's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see... Why don't you give me your\Nblueprint pieces in exchange for her life?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Big talk! If you want them,\Ncome and get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright... Take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.20,0:10:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Cursed X Rider! Be assured\NI'll have my revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Imbecile! Did I tell you to get the\Nblueprint pieces with brute force?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted you to deceive Jin\NKeisuke with your beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But... King Dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious I can't rely\Non you lot any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to take Jin Keisuke's\Nblueprint pieces myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,King Dark, are you--?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Centipede Yáng Guìfēi! Lure Jin Keisuke to the Devil's Cemetery at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast you, Jin Keisuke... This time\NI'll crush you with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going? Any clues\Nto where the girls are?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not even one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The fool has no idea he's\Nwalking right into a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Keisuke!\N-Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-So this is where you've been!\N-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke, you've fallen right into my trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I came here on\Npurpose to see your hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:14:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Yáng and his family have been in Geneva for the past week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is his daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, Jin Keisuke. But you still die\Nif you don't give me the blueprints!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh. You'll\Nnever find them without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Then I'll just\Nhave to make you talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Can't breathe...\N-Keisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ok!? ...Darn it, I can't\Nlet King Dark have his way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Great Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point transforming, X Rider.\NThose girls are as good as dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the blueprints?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll tell you\Nif you turn off the gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly! Now, out with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The blueprints... are inside Cruiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser? Alright then, call it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I've got no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruiser!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-V3!\N-Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, V3! I was so\Nclose! I will be avenged!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kazami. The blueprints\Nare safe thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. I came running when\NI heard you were in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-We're saved!\N-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to Kazami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't start celebrating yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me that blueprint if you value his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, don't worry about\Nme! You can't hand it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, there's nothing else we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to give her the blueprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what say you? Quickly, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,#2!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Curses! Another interloper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke! Shirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-Chief, I was really worried there!\N-Yeah! Don't scare us like that, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.10,0:17:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, what would you do without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I... just figured I'd take\Nmyself out of the equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Chief, is this person--?\N-Yeah, he's a Kamen Rider like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My senior: Kamen Rider #2,\NIchimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just 'Ichimonji' will do.\NYou must be the X Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke. It's\Ngood to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Three Riders all in one place!\NThere's nothing to fear now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Laugh while you can! The three of\Nthem are going to hell together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't dawdle, Centipede Yáng Guìfēi!\NTake the blueprints from his corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The X Rider's body must be in this vicinity!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right here, Centipede Yáng Guìfēi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Accursed X Rider! You survived!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ok, we'll find King Dark.\N-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-King Dark, show yourself!\N-Face us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, come, Crow Bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, come, Crow Bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, X Rider!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Vacuum Hell Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-There you are, King Dark!\N-Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.20,0:22:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Blast that King Dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.70,0:22:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not yet time for us to fight.\NBut we'll settle this soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.40,0:23:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus did Jin Keisuke defy King Dark again,\Nthanks to Kazami Shirou and Ichimonji Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But this would prove just the\Nprelude to a new challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke falls into a GOD\Ntrap and is strung up in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.30,0:23:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Toubei and the others have no choice\Nbut to give GOD their blueprint pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode,\Nfeaturing Riders #2 and V3:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Terrible Weapon Targets the Three Riders!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.16,0:23:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.76,0:23:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.66,0:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.73,0:23:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:24:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.11,0:24:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
